t: Make*p a joyful noise unto the Lord,*s all ye lands.
Serve*p the Lord*s with gladness: come before his presence with singing.
Know*p ye that the Lord*s he is God: it is he that hath made us, and not we ourselves; we are his people, and the sheep of his pasture.
